         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="Arthur-Schnitzler_an_Hermann-Bahr_00224"/><salute>Lieber Hermann,</salute> ich danke dir herzlich für dein liebes <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00852-1"/>Telegramm<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00852-1">nicht überliefert; am <ref target="1898-10-08" type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="date-only"/><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="event" ref="#pmb35382">Uraufführung von <rs ref="#pmb30219" type="work">Das Vermächtnis</rs></rs> am <rs ref="#pmb151" type="place">Deutschen Theater</rs> in <rs ref="#pmb168" type="place">Berlin</rs></note></p><closer>Dein <signed>Arth Schnitzler</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>, <date when="1898-10-14">14. X. 98</date>.</dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
